headline: State Street to Speak at the RBC Capital Markets Global Financial Institutions Conference
summary: BOSTON, February 27, 2026--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that its Chief Product Officer, Donna Milrod, and its Global Head of Strategic Finance, Mark Keating, will present at the RBC Capital Markets Global Financial Institutions Conference in New York, NY on Wednesday, March 11, 2026 at approximately 2:00 pm ET.
